{"type": "article", "id": 22324, "title": "3D打印不锈钢自行车", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143531BUOzSkXg2jvoaHf8.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是荷兰代尔夫特理工大学的学生设计团队设计的 3D 打印自行车，由 MX3D 公司协助完成。他们结合弧焊技术开发一款 3D打印机，通过电弧产生的高温熔化金属，然后制作成金属结构。车的框架结构是分别打印的，经过人工焊接，它的重量与钢架自行车一致，是探索 3D 打印中型物品的尝试。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143528KcdeO0PFEwtBjbki.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143529c8ZFB7yiw1eN0k3I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143529Ux8eXqvor5yhSHTE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143530LXzHojB2CVw7TuqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143530FJlmi3kaO2ZKwSWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}